A study on 39,040 nursing home residents (median age 84 years) and 331,039 #healthcare workers (median age 47 years) showed that 7 days after the second dose of the BNT162b2 #mRNA #COVID19 #vaccine, efficacy was 64% and 90% in the two groups, respectively.
